<textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Watch Tower</> and < textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Beach</> I think it would be ok to leave it...

20030318.text:
It's already decided, so we can't help it.
We just have to deal with it.

20030320.text:
Yes. These days, <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>coastal creatures</> have reproduced abnormally...
This is an unbearable level.

20030321.text:
I don't want to bow my head to ask from <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Yedohang</>...
It's such a difficult situation.

20030322.text: Now that I have no place to rest after work...

20030323.text: It was a pleasure to drink sake while watching the sunset...

20030324.text: (Ask if there is a nice place)

20030325.text:
It was there.
No, it is still there.

20030326.text: The view at sunset on the base <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>South Beach</> is very beautiful.

20030328.text:
It wasn't that <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>You're Dark</> wasn't there before...
It wasn't like this.

20030329.text: There aren't many, so I just had to deal with them or avoid them...

20030330.text:
These days there are so many...
I have to call them <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>You're Dark</> Beach.

20030331.text:
I can't even tell you to take all the <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Western</> crew
to clean up the beach to have a glass of sake.

20030332.text:
(They say they're sorry
the place to change their mind is gone)

20030333.text:
That's right! <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Kogondae</> also
Sometimes you need a drink to feel better...

20030334.text:
Because when you get annoyed, you just solve it for me!
I'm having a hard time. I can't say anything...

20030335.text: Oh! Is it okay if I ask for directions?

20030337.text:
I'm on my way to <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Unexplored Jadrak</> now.
Am I almost there now?

20030338.text: (I don't think it will be close)

20030342.text:
Ah~ It can be. I have a very good sense of direction.
I can't have come the other way.

20030345.text:
The world is ugly these days...
Something is wrong with the direction of the world?

20030346.text:
(Does not answer, and offers
guide you to <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Misty Forest Front</>)

20030347.text: Ah! Coming here, I think I know about it.

20030348.text:
Have you come to <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Forest of Blood</> now?
<textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Blood Plaque</> Better be careful!

20030349.text: (<textColor=[110:216:175:255]>The Forest of Blood</> is still a long way off)

20030350.text:
Huh? My sense of distance direction is something that people
stumble upon... Are you sure?

20030351.text:
(I think it's a wonderful sense of direction
but doesn't say anything)

20030353.text:
(<textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Unexpected Jadrak</>
Ask if I can go alone)

20030354.text:
No problem normally...
The world is strange these days...

20030355.text:
I would like to ask <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Younggyowon</> to
transport.

20030356.text: (he said he thought it really well)

20030358.text: (Ask if you can go with me too)

20030360.text: Speak to me when you're ready.

20030365.text: (They say it would be better to go to <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Younggyowon</> when traveling long distances in the future)

20030366.text:
Is that right? It's a little dizzy,
but it's comfortable.

20030368.text: Ah~ It's dark now. I can't see.

20030370.text: Ah! No. I was just talking to myself.

20030371.text:
Thinking about the work to be done this week...
My vision suddenly narrowed.

20030372.text:
You can't just observe <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Nakwondaeseong</>.
This is something we should do of course.

20030374.text:
Should we call it weeding?
It's a regular job of getting rid of <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Outbreak</>.

20030375.text: No. I won't be attacked and killed while pulling grass...

20030376.text: I think it would be appropriate to call it a combat insecticide.

20030377.text: Are you sure you want to come in here?

20030379.text: If you've come this far, you'll be confident in your skills...

20030380.text: You'd better watch out for the <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Flag hair</> though.

20030382.text: Can I describe it as an extremely dangerous giant monster?

20030383.text: It doesn't usually come out of its nest...

20030384.text: If you leave the nest, you're in trouble.

20030385.text:
(If you find a <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Palgfish</> nearby,
I will tell you the story)

20030386.text:
(For now, I'll tell you that I didn't see
the <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Palgfish</> around)

20030387.text:
Good luck.
There's a <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Nest</> inside over there...

20030390.text: Hey! There! Take a look here!

20030392.text: I'm making medicine right now, and I'm a little short on <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>moss</>!

20030393.text: Um... um... it's really not enough.

20030394.text: (It's okay, so I tell you to talk comfortably)

20030395.text:
Animated <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Tree Spirit</> a precious <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>Moss</>Danyang that only grows
 on the body!

20030396.text: That's a little... no need a lot!

20030397.text:
(<textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Ask if I can get 
<textColor=[255:204:102:255]>Moss</> from the Arbor</> )

20030398.text:
You can get it from
<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Arbor Spirit</> on <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Sunrise Ramp</>!

20030402.text:
No... I'd like to scrape the <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Arbor</> etc.
for an hour

20030403.text: I only got about half of this!

20030404.text: How did you do it? I want to learn too!

20030405.text: (<textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Ask if you want to scratch the back of the arboreal</>)

20030406.text:
<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>If you scratch the back of a tree spirit</>,
it feels great!

20030407.text:
(He said it wasn't really a big deal
He blurs out the end of his sentence)

20030409.text: I was patrolling nearby... Suddenly, <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Drawings</> <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Ho-Ryong Kwak</> You are there.

20030410.text: It's not our boss... but I went to greet him as a courtesy...

20030413.text: But I looked closely! This is not <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Ho-Ryong Kwak</>.

20030416.text: But... I was about to skip this one...

20030419.text: Okay! I went and said hello, but... again <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Welcome</>

20030420.text: Oh, I didn't want to go out on patrol after that.

20030422.text: (Um... Are you still not aware of your condition?)

20030423.text:
(If you're afraid of ghosts like this...
It might be better not to tell the truth)

20030424.text: (Leave me to fight the soul fire)

20030425.text: 오, 소협이군요. 안그래도 소협이 생각나던 참이었습니다.

20030427.text: <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>혈비패</>가 통행로를 습격하는 일이 잦아지고 있다는 보고입니다. 더 이상 좌시할 수 없습니다. 그래서 소협께 부탁을 하나 할까 합니다.

20030429.text: 함정을 만들어 배치할 계획입니다. <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>골짜기 바람길</>에서 <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>암각다귀의 뿔</>을 준비해주시면 나머지 재료는 저희가 준비하겠습니다.

20030430.text: 감사합니다. 소협. 덕분에 무사히 함정을 설치할 수 있었습니다.

20030432.text: 이걸로 잠시나마 통행로의 안전이 확보되었으면 좋겠네요. 자 약소한 보상을 준비했습니다. 사양말고 받아주십시오. 그럼 무운을 빌겠습니다.

20030434.text: 오, 자네. 안그래도 잘왔네. 자네한테 부탁할 게 하나 있네.

20030436.text: <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>안개 그늘 숲</>의 <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>환영</>들을 좀 처치해주게. 일꾼들이 <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>환영</>이 무서워서 도저히 일을 할 수 없다는 구만.

20030438.text: 내가 직접 나서려고 했는데, <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>내 모습을 한 환영</>도 있다지 뭔가. 영 꺼림칙해서 말이야.

20030441.text: 자네 덕분에 통행로의 안전이 어느정도 확보되었구만. 하하. 고맙네.

20030443.text: 별 일이 아니긴. 자 여기 내가 준비한 물건일세.

20030445.text: 다음에 또 부탁할 일이 있으면 자네를 찾겠네!

20030448.text: 우리는 약초를 캐러왔다냥. 그런데 주변에 <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>무서운 친구들</>이 너무 많다냥. 우리 약초꾼들을 조금만 도와달라냥.

20030451.text: 마침 잘 만났다냥! 그 <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>재수 없는 은발 머리</>는 어디 갔냥?

20030453.text: 흥. 그래도 말이 통하는 인간이 와서 다행이다냥.

20030455.text: 앗. 어떻게 알았냥!? 여기 어딘가에 <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>개다래풀</>이 있다고 한다냥. 그것 좀 구해달라냥. 이렇게 부탁한다냥.

20030466.text: <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>해월대륙</>의 자연이 절경이고 장관이라해서 왔는데, 이게 무슨 일인지 모르겠소!

20030468.text: <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>투엽단</> 놈들을 걱정했건만, 웬 <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>부패한 수양 무리</>가 밀렵을 시작했소. 이를 어쩐단 말이오! 소협의 도움이 필요하오.

20030471.text: 오, 수고했소. 덕분에 마음이 조금은 놓이는구려.

20030473.text: 뿌리 뽑진 못하겠지만, 우선 <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>수양 대장</>에게 <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>회수한 밀렵품</>을 전달해보겠소. 그럼 다음에 또 뵙겠소.

20030475.text: 오, 여기서 또 만나는 군! 여긴 어쩐 일이야?

20030477.text: 그렇군. 나는 우리, 아, 아니, <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>달빛바람</> 문주님이 보내서 왔어.

20030478.text: 그래서 말인데 나 좀 도와줄 수 있어? <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>달빛바람</>이 요구한 일정이 너무 빠듯해서 말이야...

20030480.text: 오 고맙군. 그럼 <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>낙원족이 사용하는 물건</>들 좀 구해줘. 그들이 물건도 연구 가치가 있다나...

20030482.text: 아니긴 뭐가 아니야. 이번엔 좀 직접 하라니까.

20030483.text: 에휴. 그냥 내가 <textColor=[255:204:102:255]><myHero.name/></>에게 부탁하는 게 낫겠다. 그렇지?

20030485.text: 원래는 <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>강철주먹</>이 할 일이었는데. 안되겠어. 확실한 사람한테 부탁을 해야지. <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>검은 진흙지대</>에서 <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>여러 가지 재료</>를 구해줘.

20030487.text: <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>악어 가죽, 거북이 껍질, 질긴 거미줄</>? 이정도면 간단하지?

20030490.text: 오! 소협. 여기서 또 보는 구만. 여기는 어쩐 일인가.

20030492.text: 음 그랬구만. 마침 잘됐네. <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>해맞이 행사</>를 준비해야 하는데 일손이 부족해서 말이야. 자네 손을 좀 빌릴까 하는데. 하하. 이거 원 볼때마다 부탁만 하는구만.

20030494.text: 그럼 사양않고 부탁하겠네. <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>해맞이 비탈</>에서 <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>묘면족</>의 동태를 좀 살펴주게.

20030495.text: 오 자네 왔군. 부탁이 하나 더 있네.

20030497.text: <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>해맞이 행사</>에서 날릴 <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>발발이 잎</>을 구해야는데 주변에 <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>시귀</>들이 너무 많네. <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>시귀</>를 좀 퇴치해주면 나머지는 우리가 하겠네.

20030502.text: 음, 그러셨군요. 저희 <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>에레다</>는 소협 덕분에 안정을 찾아가고 있습니다.

20030504.text: 흠... 소협을 이렇게 만난김에 민망하게도 신세를 한 번 더 질까 합니다. 괜찮겠습니까.

20030506.text: 하하, 그렇게 말씀해주시니 한결 마음이 편해지는군요. 그럼 편히 말씀 드리겠습니다.

20030507.text: 다른게 아니라 <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>검은새벽단</>이 신수를 섬기는 문파를 습격하고있습니다. 당연하게도 저희 에레다도 그 대상입니다.

20030508.text: <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>물안개 고원</>에 <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>그들의 병력</> 일부가 있다고 하여 그들을 격퇴하러 왔습니다. 소협이 힘을 보태주신다면 천군만마일 것입니다.

20030513.text: 감사하다는 말씀을 꼭 드리고 싶었습니다. 감사합니다.

20030515.text: 무거운 얘기는 여기까지 하겠습니다. 자, 그럼 임무 이야기를 해볼까요. 다름이 아니라 <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>검은새벽단</>에서 아주 끔찍한 일을 꾸미고 있다는 첩보가 있습니다.

20030517.text: <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>시귀</>를 이용하여 <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>군대</>를 만들 계획을 세우고 있는 것 같습니다. <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>시귀</>들에게 영면을 선사하여 <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>검은새벽단</>에게 이용되는 일을 막아야합니다.
